title: Aisha Tyler
description: Aisha Tyler (holy cow! the talk! archer! girl on guy podcast) is a pure delight and a weirdo treasure. Pete and Aisha had never met before, but hit it off immediately and got down to the weird, wonderful and silly, silly laugh fest that is the episode. Please enjoy you weird, weird weirdos!
